{"tid":1507425,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急］有冇記者朋友，請入黎，有幾條問題想記者朋友代為問popo","createTime":"2019-08-26T06:51:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T06:52:17.000Z","uid":274149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"02c71482b44c173067899cd70fd4565f6024d118","tid":1507425,"uid":274149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:51:53.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;代友發文&rdquo;<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n昨日黃昏在荃灣區驅散示威者的事件上，一班穿着白色T恤手臂綁有紅繩或藍色T恤的人士在現場毆打示威者，其中一格的士車尾箱有大量鐵通，而在場的軍裝警察並無制止。<br />\n<br />\n問題 一<br />\n想請問警方在昨日荃灣行動中有沒有聘請或邀請其他社團或非警務人員協助處理驅散示威者行動？<br />\n<br />\n問題 二<br />\n想請問運載鐵通的的士因為玻璃被示威者打破，因為佢地係幫警方驅散示威者，該車輛是否得到警方賠償？<br />\n<br />\n問題 三<br />\n想請問手執國旗支持警察，就得到警方庇護，可以隨時毆打市民？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f99949a5c175c99a3ec17f8aa4001a2bd12a667d","tid":1507425,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:52:06.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY0lZDiKRLpOq3%2FNqhGVOPOo%3D&h=133a5390\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"85ccc48ca81f9071e96e030813cce05166cb7c94","tid":1507425,"uid":56052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:52:17.000Z","msg":"(外國文宣) 大家係咪miss 左一粒核彈？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1507386\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1507386</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}